"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56692976\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"cursor: default; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>Eldhusid餐厅</a></span></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"380518921\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/105930.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"霍芬\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">霍芬</a>&nbsp;龙虾餐厅，网红餐厅，对于到处吃龙虾的我们也去体验了一下。晚餐，餐厅里并没有那么多客人，没有预订，坐在靠窗的位置，点了虾尾汤、带虾钳的龙虾和纯虾身。味道、新鲜度都没有惊艳的感觉，就是餐量比较大。一餐价格￥1000+，“性价比太低，比澳洲龙虾差远了”&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/6.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380500029.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/76/5D/wKgED1uu35WAMbNOAAcg7tvt4Js20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/76/5D/wKgED1uu35WAMbNOAAcg7tvt4Js20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/76/5D/wKgED1uu35WAMbNOAAcg7tvt4Js20.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380500029\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56692952\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"cursor: default; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>霍芬龙虾餐厅</a></span></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"380564931\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">旅行中购买当地食材自己做饭，对于我们来说是一大乐趣，每次出去都会带一些调料现场烹饪。在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>早餐和晚餐自己做，午餐是路餐，或者做好了食物找个风景好的地方野餐。我们做过煎牛排、猪排和不同种类的鱼，蘑菇炒肉、咖喱土豆、黑胡椒洋葱、煎西红柿口味都很不错，主食有面包、米饭和意面，水果最爱蓝莓和梨，每餐保证水果、蔬菜、鸡蛋、肉类和谷物都有。&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>&nbsp;食物资源和天朝是没法比的，每家酒店提供的、超市能买到的、餐厅吃到的无外乎也就这些品种了。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380530845.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAX9A1ABZO_mRQ9k471.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAX9A1ABZO_mRQ9k471.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAX9A1ABZO_mRQ9k471.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380530845\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380530848.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAVOvhABIuVsVZWQs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAVOvhABIuVsVZWQs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/99/6B/wKgED1uu8DaAVOvhABIuVsVZWQs68.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380530848\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"></h2><p><br/></p>', 'dan', 0000000001, '2019-05-17 18:23:45', '那些好吃的东西', '临沂市', '兰山区', '山东省临沂市兰山区area1', 0, 0, '关于美食很遗憾，魏司机吃了两顿 冰岛 餐就强烈要求吃我做的饭！一定要点评呢，就按', 'ArticleImg/2019/05/17/佐伊_EtEzixn.jpg'), (4, '山东省', 1, '城市打卡', '<h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">路况</span></h2><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"380134586\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">1号公路就不用点评了，那是众所周知的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>&nbsp;最好路况，唯一的环岛公路，铺装路，单车道，中间高两边低，开车容易跑偏&nbsp;<img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/12.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;。偶尔也有一小段沙石路，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"比如\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">比如</a>&nbsp;贝鲁峡湾8公里沙石路。<br/>两位数 、三位数的公路几乎全是沙石路，也有不错的铺装路。有些路面比较平整，有些起伏颠簸不平。不过我们觉得也要看位置，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16084.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雷克雅未克\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">雷克雅未克</a>&nbsp;大区、斯奈山半岛、南部、东部的公路就不错，而北部峡湾公路就有待修缮，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63871.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西峡\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西峡</a>&nbsp;湾路况最差。<br/>F级公路就不用说了，想进入先检查车辆，加满油，做好心理建设。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380129640.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C3/wKgED1utqvGAO1eZABSOmW7RDu068.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C3/wKgED1utqvGAO1eZABSOmW7RDu068.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C3/wKgED1utqvGAO1eZABSOmW7RDu068.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380129640\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56693936\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"cursor: default; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>Þjórsárdalur</a></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380130015.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/FD/wKgED1utqzSAGy_jABBvYkH56Ro95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/FD/wKgED1utqzSAGy_jABBvYkH56Ro95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/FD/wKgED1utqzSAGy_jABBvYkH56Ro95.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380130015\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/141672.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>西峡湾区</a></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380129647.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/40/DC/wKgED1uqKr6Adey7AA9CxpSRw0Y61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/40/DC/wKgED1uqKr6Adey7AA9CxpSRw0Y61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/40/DC/wKgED1uqKr6Adey7AA9CxpSRw0Y61.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380129647\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/8536432.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"8536432\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>兰德曼纳劳卡</a></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380129645.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C4/wKgED1utqvKAYpwVABKubrJ-ZJA46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C4/wKgED1utqvKAYpwVABKubrJ-ZJA46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B7/C4/wKgED1utqvKAYpwVABKubrJ-ZJA46.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380129645\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56693936\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"cursor: default; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>Þjórsárdalur</a></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10549/scenery_10703402/380130050.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/84/FA/wKgED1um6vqARQfqAA3efmTLyyo52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/84/FA/wKgED1um6vqARQfqAA3efmTLyyo52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/84/FA/wKgED1um6vqARQfqAA3efmTLyyo52.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"380130050\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 480px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56692352\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"cursor: default; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>斯奈山半岛</a></span></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"380129642\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>&nbsp;的各条公路不是全年开放，很多峡湾公路、内陆公路、F级公路只有在夏季短暂开放。政府也有很多修路、修桥计划，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"比如\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">比如</a>&nbsp;从&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/105922.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"胡萨维克\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">胡萨维克</a>&nbsp;到&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65453.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"米湖\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">米湖</a>&nbsp;的87号公路11公里修路路段就非常难走，还要停车等候；去丁迪扬瀑布的60号公路大部分路段都在修路；有些单行桥维修时，也要等候红绿灯放行。以上路况信息可以在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>&nbsp;路况网站&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.road.is/\" data-kw=\"http://www.road.is/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px;\">http://www.road.is/</a>&nbsp;或者在Vegagerdin这个APP上提前关注。下文会详细介绍。</p><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">隧道</span></h2><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"380881872\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在北部峡湾，我们第一次遇到双向行驶只有一条车道的隧道，一侧有20多个间断的停车区。进入隧道前有黑红箭头指示，黑色箭头方向车辆顺行，红色箭头方向车辆让行，遇到会车时红色方向车辆停入停车区等候让行。我们刚刚开进隧道时，黑乎乎的隧道里前后都没有车，还以为自己走了逆行，看到停车区才反应过来。<br/>在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/141672.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西峡湾区\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西峡湾区</a>&nbsp;，经过&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62908.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"伊萨菲厄泽\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊萨菲厄泽</a>&nbsp;60号公路进入&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62908.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"伊萨菲厄泽\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊萨菲厄泽</a>&nbsp;-萨杜雷里-弗拉泰里隧道，一条&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/124642.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"三出\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">三出</a>&nbsp;口隧道，建成于1996年。&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62908.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"伊萨菲厄泽\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊萨菲厄泽</a>&nbsp;往弗拉泰里方向隧道6公里，大部分是双向单车道隧道，一侧是间隔停车区。走到中间位置，隧道一分为二，另一条通向3公里外的萨杜雷里，仍然是双向单车道隧道，一侧是间隔停车区。感觉这样的隧道设计有创意，在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10549.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"冰岛\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">冰岛</a>&nbsp;这样的环境&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10689.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中非\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中非</a>&nbsp;常实用，如果换在帝都估计隧道早就被挤爆了。</p><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"></h2><p><br/></p>', 'dan', 0000000000, '2019-05-17 18:23:55', '城市打卡', '临沂市', '河东区', '山东省临沂市河东区area0', 0, 0, '在大象孤儿院喂大象是我mark的一定要做的事情！Pinnawala离Negomb', 'ArticleImg/2019/05/17/Reflection-4.jpg'), (5, '山东省', 0, '徒步旅行', '<h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.	制定徒步路线要根据目的地的季节选择</h3><p>不同季节的景色是不同的，例如，黄石的夏季与冬季是截然不同的两种风貌；落基山的秋天适宜徒步，冬天的景色也非常迷人。</p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/27/wKgED1wx6rWAXExmAASnUepKrU841.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/27/wKgED1wx6rWAXExmAASnUepKrU841.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/27/wKgED1wx6rWAXExmAASnUepKrU841.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 300px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">图片来源于网络</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.	量力而行</h3><p>出行前一定要做强度评估，测算路线的时间与距离，根据自己的体力选择路线，不要多度自信。很多徒步路线都在高海拔，要把此类因素都考虑在内。</p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/37/wKgED1wx6sWAWVQcAAN7sl6uBQ842.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/37/wKgED1wx6sWAWVQcAAN7sl6uBQ842.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/23/37/wKgED1wx6sWAWVQcAAN7sl6uBQ842.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 340px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">图片来源于网络</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.	充分利用公家公园游客中心</h3><p>在游客中心可以获得路线等信息，出发前也应查询好，路线附近的游客中心都有哪些，可以去寻求帮助。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/D6/wKgED1wx6eGAEcfCAANWhjaqnes69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/D6/wKgED1wx6eGAEcfCAANWhjaqnes69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/D6/wKgED1wx6eGAEcfCAANWhjaqnes69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">图片来源于网络</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.	许可制度</h3><p>美国国家公园大多有许可制度，一般多日徒步，需要露营扎宅时需要申请。每个公园的制度和可申请时间都不太一样，大多是先到先得的方式。如果预约了公园内的酒店住宿，则不必担心这个问题。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/18/wKgED1wx6V6AWgdxAAODMVdThbU35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/18/wKgED1wx6V6AWgdxAAODMVdThbU35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/18/wKgED1wx6V6AWgdxAAODMVdThbU35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 340px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">图片来源于网络</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.	不要做独行侠</h3><p>徒步一定要有同行人，可以在平台寻找志同道合的小伙伴，也可以选择旅行社的陪同服务。尤其是对徒步入门的旅行者，一定要有老司机带路。想要看尽多日徒步景色，又不想过于辛苦的旅行者，可以选择向导和挑夫服务。</p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/3A/wKgED1wx6XOAaldrAAO6pmNbW3883.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/3A/wKgED1wx6XOAaldrAAO6pmNbW3883.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/21/3A/wKgED1wx6XOAaldrAAO6pmNbW3883.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">图片来源于网络</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6.购买境外保险</h3><p>境外旅行一定要买保险！境外旅行一定要买保险！境外旅行一定要买保险！计划徒步旅行，与平常普通的境外旅行保险相比，可以挑选更适合户外的险种，出行前应仔细了解保险的内容。</p><p><br/></p>', 'dan', 0000000000, '2019-05-17 18:24:04', '徒步旅行', '淄博市', '淄川区', '山东省淄博市淄川区', 0, 0, '不同季节的景色是不同的，例如，黄石的夏季与冬季是截然不同的两种风貌；落基山的秋天', 'ArticleImg/2019/05/17/Reflection-2.jpg'), (6, '山东省', 2, 'Part1 （景点篇）', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Part1 （景点篇）</h3><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">一步一景，这里处处是天然影棚</h3><p>东山，一座几年前还是养在深闺人未识的神秘感小岛，大多数人的初次遇见，都是通过荧屏，包括小爱我。这里曾拍过《西游记》《八仙过海》《我是谁的宝贝》等影视作品，但真正被大家深挖的时间基本是2015年苏有朋拍摄的电影《左耳》。多少人追着电影的情节，跟着《左耳》去旅行，我也算其中一个。看来名人效应的作用，这个年代还是有用的哈哈。<br/><br/>要不，小爱带着大家看看我去过的地方？follow&nbsp;me&nbsp;~<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F0/27/wKgED1ukUHCAEqlVAAA8Tkr5-fE03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F0/27/wKgED1ukUHCAEqlVAAA8Tkr5-fE03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F0/27/wKgED1ukUHCAEqlVAAA8Tkr5-fE03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 320px; width: 480px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">电影《左耳》拍摄地</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第一站苏峰山：</strong><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">蓝色环岛路桥，网红打卡新晋地</strong><br/><br/>今年随着抖音大热，东山岛又有一处私密地点被大众所知，那就是苏峰山。爱拍照的女生当然不能错过啦，厦门有环岛路这里也有，厦门有海湾公园这里也有，海边城市都是这么命名的么？没有新意哈哈哈。但很多人不知道，东山岛是以此山而得名的。</p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/03/12/wKgED1ukXUqAFvnUAA_2Eipe0tk526.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/03/12/wKgED1ukXUqAFvnUAA_2Eipe0tk526.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/03/12/wKgED1ukXUqAFvnUAA_2Eipe0tk526.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 426px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">苏峰山</span></p><p>其实我觉得面朝大海的日子就特别容易滋生出文艺浪漫的情怀，在东山岛，桥是蓝色的，房子是彩色的，海是绿色的，生活在东山岛上的人，面向太平洋，不经意间就把天空和大海的颜色都融进了日子里。<br/></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第二站南门湾：</strong><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">一半海岸一半城，渔村文艺换新颜</strong><br/><br/>大噪一时的电影《左耳》，其主要取景地就在南门湾！电影给我留下最深印象的就是，沙滩上女主角痛哭流涕的场景。身后的南门湾，一边是蔚蓝的大海，一边是古朴的渔村。<br/><br/>彩色的房子，面朝大海的生活，我想，住在这里的人一定都很温暖吧。住不了这里，那我就选择租个小电驴，吹着海风，穿梭在彩色的画面里，美滋滋。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F1/A2/wKgED1ukUZCAZVUjABGprlqevgU626.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F1/A2/wKgED1ukUZCAZVUjABGprlqevgU626.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F1/A2/wKgED1ukUZCAZVUjABGprlqevgU626.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 451px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">南门湾</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第三站顶街：</strong><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">一条古街，可赏一路明清风</strong><br/><br/>大家可千万别小看这条街，顶街可是明清两朝的官路哦。走在这条小路上会有种在历史长廊的感觉，两侧是各具特色的明清建筑建筑，有古厝有宫庙有故居，名人的家在这里稀松平常。如果你来到东山铜陵镇，一定不能错过这条依山傍海的古香古味的老街，走进老巷弄，触摸一道道古门，撸撸小巷里慵懒的小喵咪，放缓脚步感受这座小岛。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/09/wKgED1ukUdKAWNdSAAJ7a4uGCsw01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/09/wKgED1ukUdKAWNdSAAJ7a4uGCsw01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/09/wKgED1ukUdKAWNdSAAJ7a4uGCsw01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 512px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第四站马銮湾+金銮湾：</strong><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">天然浴场，海上极乐世界</strong><br/><br/>来东山，一定要好好看的就是海啊，热门推荐就是马銮湾和金銮湾了。汪涵主持的《我们来了》节目，就选择了马銮湾帆船训练基地作为一个重要的拍摄点。这里除了拥有平坦的沙滩、干净的海水以及良好的避风海湾之外，更是汇聚了非常多有趣的海洋体验项目，比如帆船、风筝冲浪、浮潜、沙排、摩托艇、快艇、水上自行车等等。当然你也可以选择到此游泳，在海里玩个酣畅淋漓。<br/><br/>金銮湾有什么不同呢？其实，两个地方相隔不远，但是金銮湾更安静，周边也有不少比较高端的度假公寓和别墅可选，但是要玩水上项目的记得去马銮湾呦。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1ukZAGAOBsrAAFHnCfCfEg28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1ukZAGAOBsrAAFHnCfCfEg28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1ukZAGAOBsrAAFHnCfCfEg28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 452px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">海上帆船</span></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/CC/wKgED1ukUmaAdxnXAEdsX_Gk6vw265.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/CC/wKgED1ukUmaAdxnXAEdsX_Gk6vw265.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F2/CC/wKgED1ukUmaAdxnXAEdsX_Gk6vw265.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">快艇巡游东山岛</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Part2（住宿篇）</h3><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">在诗意之地的民宿里，体验当地生活</h3><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F3/E7/wKgED1ukUvyAZxOCAAHog51vmus709.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F3/E7/wKgED1ukUvyAZxOCAAHog51vmus709.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/F3/E7/wKgED1ukUvyAZxOCAAHog51vmus709.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 507px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p>在东山，住宿体验也是一种旅行享受。这里的房子面朝大海，推门即海的场景在这里不断上演，是不是有点羡慕？不用羡慕啦，在这住一晚很简单的，好好感受这里的风和日丽。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/04/2D/wKgED1ukXg2ANIoHAAd7qslndwE11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/04/2D/wKgED1ukXg2ANIoHAAd7qslndwE11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/04/2D/wKgED1ukXg2ANIoHAAd7qslndwE11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 967px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">东山岛一隅</span></p><p>在南门湾和马銮湾周边比较多的是公寓和民宿，而金銮湾附近则比较多的是酒店和度假村，根据个人喜好选择即可，在网络上都可以预定到的，价格也都算实惠啦。想要舒适度和景观好一些的，我就推荐我住过的米兰春天啦，高楼层的海景一定不会让你失望的。<br/></p><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/08/31/wKgED1ukYO-ANDqIAAW_y1DfY9A700.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/08/31/wKgED1ukYO-ANDqIAAW_y1DfY9A700.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/08/31/wKgED1ukYO-ANDqIAAW_y1DfY9A700.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 515px; width: 674px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">东山米兰酒店</strong><br/>位置：&nbsp;金銮湾庄园御海9-01号楼&nbsp;<br/>特色：出门即是大海，高层海景房视野超棒<br/>价格：&nbsp;平日200-400元/晚<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=102&hotel_id=9204316\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_quote_guide\" data-title=\"东山米兰酒店\" data-id=\"9204316\" data-type=\"2\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 680px; height: 153px; position: relative;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=102&hotel_id=9204316\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_quote_guide\" data-title=\"东山米兰酒店\" data-id=\"9204316\" data-type=\"2\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 680px; height: 153px; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/F2/C9/wKgBpVWbsyKAWJTOAACCnHJ8Ejc71.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21240x240r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21240x240%2Fquality%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 236px;\"/></a></p><h2 style=\"margin: 18px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: normal; line-height: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=102&hotel_id=9204316\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_quote_guide\" data-title=\"东山米兰酒店\" data-id=\"9204316\" data-type=\"2\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 680px; height: 153px; position: relative;\">东山米兰酒店</a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-line-clamp: 4; max-height: 81px; line-height: 21px;\"><a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=102&hotel_id=9204316\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_quote_guide\" data-title=\"东山米兰酒店\" data-id=\"9204316\" data-type=\"2\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 680px; height: 153px; position: relative;\">酒店无论是设施齐备的标准客房，亦或是全方位拎包入住体验的公寓式套房一应俱全。在这里，绵长柔软的沙滩，湛蓝清澈的海水，扑鼻而来的浪漫气息。困扰城市的PM2.5在这里毫无影踪，留下的只有纯净的空气和原生态的景色体验。细节处的精心设计，以及欧式低调不乏时尚元素的装修风格，让您随时随地都有惊喜发现。身处东山岛，怎能少的了海鲜大餐的加盟？酒店全日制餐厅塞纳宫将为您奉上地道的当地美食以及中西结合的餐饮文化。傍晚时分，您可以去到我们户外的专属沙滩加入热情洋溢的BBQ烤肉派对，在欣赏天然景色的同时，满足您的味蕾。</a></p><p><br/></p><p><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">光明顶初海民宿</strong><br/>位置：风动石景区附近的山腰上<br/>特色：房子是80年代闽南石头建筑结构，3个看海露台，公共空间可做饭、烧烤、看电影<br/>价格：平日260元/晚</p><p><br/></p>', 'dan', 0000000000, '2019-05-17 18:24:12', 'Part1景点篇', '淄博市', '张店区', '山东省淄博市张店区', 0, 0, 'Part1 （景点篇） 一步一景，这里处处是天然影棚 东山，一座几年前还是养在深', 'ArticleImg/2019/05/17/Reflection-1.jpg'), (7, '江苏省', 1, '禁止或限制入境的物品', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin: 18px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">禁止或限制入境的物品</h2><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/BF/8F/wKgEaVzGnNKAHYkeAAAqODP09z444.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/BF/8F/wKgEaVzGnNKAHYkeAAAqODP09z444.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/BF/8F/wKgEaVzGnNKAHYkeAAAqODP09z444.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 300px; width: 400px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">a.枪支和武器：</h3><p><br/>所有必须向加拿大边境服务局申报。<br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">b.食品、植物、动物以及相关物品</h3><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C0/2A/wKgEaVzGnSqAfhr9AAgJyVie3tI27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C0/2A/wKgEaVzGnSqAfhr9AAgJyVie3tI27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C0/2A/wKgEaVzGnSqAfhr9AAgJyVie3tI27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 455px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p>必须全部申报。为了防止生态系统被破坏，各种病菌入侵带来的损害，加拿大对肉制品、蔬菜、水果、植物等都有限制，建议避免携带入境。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">c.车辆</h3><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/F8/wKgEaVzGnn6AeljSAACfbAw94ww73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/F8/wKgEaVzGnn6AeljSAACfbAw94ww73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/F8/wKgEaVzGnn6AeljSAACfbAw94ww73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 416px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p>包括轿车、皮卡、雪地摩托以及房车，只要是非商业用途的，都有很多限制。<br/>可以访问以下网址查看：<a href=\"http://cbsa.gc.ca/publications/dm-md/d19/d19-12-1-eng.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">http://cbsa.gc.ca/publications/dm-md/d19/d19-12-1-eng.html</a><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">d.消费品</h3><p>加拿大人对消费品有着极高的安全要求，有些甚至要比其他国家的安全要求严格。某些消费品的进口可能会对公众构成危害，因而是被禁止的，比如说婴儿学步车。<br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">e.礼品</h3><p>如果要给在加拿大的朋友带一些礼物，那么免税限额为不超过60加元的物品，但是烟酒，以及广告品不能作为礼品申报。超出免税限额的部分需要缴纳。<br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">f.炸药、烟火和弹药</h3><p>如有携带此类物品，你必须持有允许携带炸药、烟火，以及弹药型号的书面授权和许可。<br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">g.处方药</h3><p><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/D4/wKgEaVzGnnGAS_G6AABOXcpclOc56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/D4/wKgEaVzGnnGAS_G6AABOXcpclOc56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/C2/D4/wKgEaVzGnnGAS_G6AABOXcpclOc56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin: 10px 0px; display: block; height: 335px; width: 578px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><span class=\"img-an\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"></span></p><p>在加拿大，健康产品的的监管制度可能和别的国家不同，因此，如果要带处方药入境，该药品必须带有原始的标签和使用说明，以及医生的处方。如果没有上述说明，则带上处方的复印件或者医生的说明。</p><p><br/></p>', 'dan', 0000000000, '2019-05-17 18:24:41', '禁止或限制入境的物品', '南京市', '玄武区', '江苏省南京市玄武区', 0, 0, '加拿大人对消费品有着极高的安全要求，有些甚至要比其他国家的安全要求严格。某些消费', 'ArticleImg/2019/05/17/Flower-6.jpg'), (8, '江苏省', 2, '水瓶和射手的行前准备', '<h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">水瓶和射手的行前准备</span></h2><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"421827296\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">3月底我和维尼说我离职了，于是我们就定了去&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"泰国\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>&nbsp;的机票，时间很赶我们选择了落地签，出发前一天才去银行兑泰铢，然后被告知小币种要预约，于是在浦东机场兑了一些，不得不说机场的汇率真的是有点坑，我们就兑了5000铢，办理落地签时用。<br/></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_11696426/421831464.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1xGzs-APLNEABQ_AQwD9LQ45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1xGzs-APLNEABQ_AQwD9LQ45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/0D/03/wKgED1xGzs-APLNEABQ_AQwD9LQ45.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"421831464\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6116492.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6116492\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>清迈古城</a></span></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"421831466\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;时间：2018年4月3日——2018年4月11日<br/><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;地点：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清迈\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清迈</a>&nbsp;（4天）、&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/24711.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"华欣\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">华欣</a>&nbsp;（2天）、&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;（3天）<br/><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;必备APP：Grab（打车软件）、Google Maps（我在国内下载好了用不了，到了之后重新下载才能用）、Google 翻译<br/>大众点评在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"泰国\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>&nbsp;很好用，我们的第一顿就是大众点评上找的，巨好吃！总之在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"泰国\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>&nbsp;吃的就踩了一次雷，还是在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;的时候路过一家烤猪蹄店，被香味欺骗了去吃，很油腻<br/><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;必带物品：药（尤其是拉肚子的药）、防晒霜（必须50+）、长袖薄外套（&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"泰国\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>&nbsp;的寺庙对女生有穿着要求，不能露肩，裙子短裤不等短于膝盖）、手机防水袋、手机卡、泰铢（落地签2000/人）</p><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">机票酒店</span></h2><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"421838459\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;机票：<br/><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"上海\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上海</a>&nbsp;——&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清迈\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清迈</a>&nbsp;（977rmb/人），&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清迈\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清迈</a>&nbsp;——&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;（420rmb/人），&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;——&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"上海\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上海</a>&nbsp;（982rmb/人）<br/>机票都是出发前一周在飞猪上定的，往返&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"上海\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上海</a>&nbsp;都是春秋航空，行李限15公斤，所以回来的时候我们买了20公斤的行李额，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清迈\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清迈</a>&nbsp;飞&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;选的是&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"泰国\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>&nbsp;国际航空。<br/>市内交通基本上都是tutu车，出租车，tutu可以还价的<br/><br/><img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/208.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;酒店：<br/>酒店对比了booking，&nbsp;<a href=\"https://airbnbchina.cn/?af=19290329&c=mfw_airbnb_hyperlink_general?keyword=airbnb\" data-kw=\"airbnb\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px;\">airbnb</a>&nbsp;等，最后在马蜂窝上定了，定的迟了几家想住的网红酒店都满房了orz<br/><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清迈\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清迈</a>&nbsp;：M HOTEL，这个酒店位置没得挑，出门就是&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424032.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_poi\" data-kw=\"塔佩门\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">塔佩门</a>&nbsp;，附近吃的巨多，还可以接机<br/><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/24711.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"华欣\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">华欣</a>&nbsp;：拉帕&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/24711.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"华欣\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">华欣</a>&nbsp;酒店，位置也是很好，走过去沙滩几分钟，有泳池环境很棒，不过我们还是后悔为什么没有定就在海边的希尔顿<br/><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11045.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"曼谷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曼谷</a>&nbsp;城市酒店，位置很好，几大商圈都可以步行<br/><br/>原谅我没有拍酒店的习惯，前方多图预警</p><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px center; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal; line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anc