fengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436199184.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/C8/wKgEaVx8lJCAE1mfABH7_eCKh_E10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/C8/wKgEaVx8lJCAE1mfABH7_eCKh_E10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/C8/wKgEaVx8lJCAE1mfABH7_eCKh_E10.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"436199184\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"436199248\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">从千厮门大桥看洪崖洞，确实很美，不过之后我走到了洪崖洞最下面。拍摄，觉得那个机位拍摄洪崖洞才是最好看的，不多说，上图。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436199185.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/CB/wKgEaVx8lJKAZkKqABIRJlw51y818.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/CB/wKgEaVx8lJKAZkKqABIRJlw51y818.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7F/CB/wKgEaVx8lJKAZkKqABIRJlw51y818.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"436199185\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"436199414\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">周五晚上的洪崖洞真的是人山人海，建议直接坐电梯下楼到最底层，然后一层一层逛上来，不然你辛辛苦苦挤下去，还想再挤上去去解放碑那边，基本精力就耗费完了。洪崖洞就是吃吃喝喝一条街，各种火锅、小吃，夜景很好看，吃饭的话，我自己因为一个人火锅就放弃了，选择了去八一美食街。<br/></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436200217.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/81/41/wKgEaVx8lXeATQN3AA1_FjeFZrY33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/81/41/wKgEaVx8lXeATQN3AA1_FjeFZrY33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/81/41/wKgEaVx8lXeATQN3AA1_FjeFZrY33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"436200217\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"436200383\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">打卡了解放碑之后，我去了八一美食街买了点吃的。听朋友介绍，可以去一座写字楼楼上免费看&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"重庆\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>的夜景，于是我就听着他的介绍，去了那栋写字楼，楼顶封住了，但是在下面的几层，照样也看到了&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"重庆\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>&nbsp;超级赞的夜景。可以看到IFC，还有威斯汀。<br/></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436200709.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/82/00/wKgEaVx8lgKAT_LzAAX9H45Zb2U60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/82/00/wKgEaVx8lgKAT_LzAAX9H45Zb2U60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/82/00/wKgEaVx8lgKAT_LzAAX9H45Zb2U60.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"436200709\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436200710.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: p